Title: On Brane Actions and Superembeddings

Authors: P.S. Howe, O. Raetzel and E. Sezgin

Comments: 19 pages, latex

Journal-ref: JHEP 9808 (1998) 011

Actions for branes, with or without worldsurface gauge fields, are discussedin a unified framework. A simple algorithm is given for constructing thecomponent Green-Schwarz actions. Superspace actions are also discussed. Threeand the D2-brane, which both have on-shell worldsurface supermultiplets, andthe membrane in D=4, which has an off-shell multiplet.